Comment: 0,0:22:20.76,0:22:28.02,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to'oi kumo no you ni  tsukamenai anata ni
Comment: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:35.86,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tsuite-yuku  doko-made mo  kokoro ni chikatte
Comment: 0,0:22:36.02,0:22:39.78,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}itsuka subete ga wakatte mo
Comment: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:43.83,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}anata o suki de irareru-koto
Comment: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:51.63,RMLyrics2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}tatoe tatakau mainichi ni  akekurete mo
